; Horner's method: 3x^3 + 2x^2 + 5x + 7 at x = 11
; Slot 0 holds x.
; Algorithm (left-to-right Horner):
;   ((3*x + 2)*x + 5)*x + 7
; At x=11:
;   (((3*11 + 2) * 11 + 5) * 11 + 7)
;   = ((35) * 11 + 5) * 11 + 7
;   = (385 + 5) * 11 + 7
;   = 390 * 11 + 7
;   = 4290 + 7
;   = 4297  ✓
PUSH 11
STORE 0
LOAD 0
PUSH 3
MUL
PUSH 2
ADD
LOAD 0
MUL
PUSH 5
ADD
LOAD 0
MUL
PUSH 7
ADD
PRINT
HALT
